The paper focuses on automated unit testing for embedded software, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The paper also discusses the implementation of a new tool, which involves programming languages and compilers (cs.PL) and system-level design and implementation (cs.SY). The paper also evaluates the effectiveness of the tool in finding runtime exceptions, which relates to computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
